 and existing fans.\", \"from\": 376, \"to\": 509, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 449, \"end\": 454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999908732207, \"rank\": 9.126797315859887e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Breaking's adherents underwent a period of soul searching after it was added to the Paris program, questioning whether their beloved dance could translate to an Olympic audience while maintaining its roots.\", \"from\": 511, \"to\": 717, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 595, \"end\": 600, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999908732207, \"rank\": 9.126797315859887e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That conundrum will play out in the broadcast booth, where David Shreibman - also known as b-boy Kid David - says he must cater to two very different types of viewers.\", \"from\": 719, \"to\": 886, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are talking to all the b-boys and b-girls and people involved in hip hop culture around the world that have watched this before, but we are also talking to a mainstream audience,\\\" he told Reuters.\", \"from\": 888, \"to\": 1088, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1080, \"end\": 1087, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 0.9999999873391517, \"rank\": 1.2645891724847576e-08, \"text\": \"Reuters\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not like commentating basketball where, you know, people have a base understanding of the game.\", \"from\": 1090, \"to\": 1191, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are starting from scratch.\\\"\", \"from\": 1192, \"to\": 1222, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympics are no stranger to niche sports: the Games make room for smaller operations such as marathon swimming and trampoline gymnastics alongside bigger sports like track and field.\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1410, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1343, \"end\": 1364, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trampolining\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"trampoline gymnastics\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trampolining\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trampolining\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But breaking has a narrow window of time to take advantage of the Olympic spotlight after it was dropped from the Los Angeles 2028 program.\", \"from\": 1412, \"to\": 1551, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1526, \"end\": 1542, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2028_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Los Angeles 2028\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2028_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2028_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Shreibman, who will be a play-by-play commentator for U.S. broadcaster NBC, said he would address both a cultural and generational divide, with large swathes of American viewers still prone to using the passe term \\\"breakdancing\\\".\", \"from\": 1553, \"to\": 1782, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1624, \"end\": 1627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9908680708308178, \"rank\": 0.009048227397600053, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 1714, \"end\": 1722, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9197327091454008, \"rank\": 0.08707509216033073, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am talking to people that think breaking stopped in the '80s,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1784, \"to\": 1858, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am excited for people to see where it's gone and explain it.\\\"\", \"from\": 1859, \"to\": 1923, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A commentator for the Red Bull BC One championships, he will adjust his tactics for the broader television audience this time, with an eye towards bringing in more fans.\", \"from\": 1925, \"to\": 2094, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1947, \"end\": 1962, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Red_Bull_BC_One\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Red Bull BC One\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Red_Bull_BC_One\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Red_Bull_BC_One\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am basically judging, commentating and educating at the same time,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2096, \"to\": 2175, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's most important to explain to the people at home what's going on.\", \"from\": 2176, \"to\": 2246, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"How is this judged?\", \"from\": 2247, \"to\": 2266, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Why is that good?\", \"from\": 2267, \"to\": 2284, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Why was that bad?\\\"\", \"from\": 2285, \"to\": 2303, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris Olympic breaking competition begins on August 9 at La Concorde.- Rappler.com  How does this make you feel?\", \"from\": 2305, \"to\": 2421, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2309, \"end\": 2314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999908732207, \"rank\": 9.126797315859887e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2380, \"end\": 2391, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resourc